messages.msgSnippet: Wow -- we d end up in the middle of the Indian Ocean, east of Madagascar.  Both our boys, especially Andy, love to dig holes (I have one 3 deep in my yard
messages.messageBody:
Wow -- we'd end up in the middle of the Indian Ocean, east of Madagascar. Both our boys, especially Andy, love to dig holes (I have one 3' deep in my yard right now). I showed the 'other side location' to the boys and suggested we'd need underwater gear. Andy said, "Yeah, but that's only after we go thru the earth's core, where we'd need a sunhat." I'm thinking maybe more than a sunhat.

What a very cool link -- thanks for sharing, Kelly!

Sylvia
